query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS publication_log (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  claimId INT NOT NULL,
  tribunalRunId INT,
  publishedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  gitSha VARCHAR(64),
  datasetVintageIds JSON,
  publishedBy VARCHAR(100),
  publishType ENUM('auto', 'manual_override') DEFAULT 'auto',
  overrideReason TEXT,
  pageContext VARCHAR(255),
  INDEX idx_claim (claimId),
  INDEX idx_published (publishedAt)
);
